file.name: issue1086.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.0.0
  title: "test"
components:
  schemas:
    AssessCandidate:
      type: object
      properties:
        candidate:
          type: object
          properties:
            id:
              type: string
          required:
            - id
        test_results:
          type: object
          properties:
            id:
              type: string
            status:
              type: string
            score:
              type: number
              multipleOf: 1
            date:
              type: string
              format: date
            comment:
              type: string
            result_url:
              type: string
      required:
        - candidate
        - test_results
